pride is just a dangerous,

01:23:28.440 --> 01:23:31.320
I guess it's a dangerous drug for me

01:23:31.320 --> 01:23:34.160
because like it's such a small,

01:23:36.560 --> 01:23:38.040
it's a small step away

01:23:38.040 --> 01:23:39.920
from then losing all the humility

01:23:39.920 --> 01:23:42.440
and then you started getting very defensive

01:23:42.440 --> 01:23:43.640
and that's not going to,

01:23:43.640 --> 01:23:47.560
that just starts you on a spiral of negative emotion.

01:23:47.560 --> 01:23:50.560
But I also, I mean, with everybody,

01:23:50.560 --> 01:23:51.400
you mentioned this,

