Again, disagreeing with an expert here.

01:28:00.760 --> 01:28:02.920
Yes, I think that's generally good advice,

01:28:02.920 --> 01:28:05.480
but I think you mentioned vulnerability.

01:28:07.280 --> 01:28:10.600
