01:28:10.600 --> 01:28:12.840
on rocket engines and fuel.

01:28:12.840 --> 01:28:16.800
And speaking of fuel, I just think I get a lot

01:28:16.800 --> 01:28:19.120
from being vulnerable because vulnerable leads

01:28:19.120 --> 01:28:22.080
to intimacy in friendships and relationships.

01:28:22.080 --> 01:28:24.640
I get a lot from being intimately close with human beings,

01:28:24.640 --> 01:28:29.200
just on a friendship, on like a ideal level

01:28:29.200 --> 01:28:31.080
in conversations and so on.

01:28:31.080 --> 01:28:36.080
And so I would rather err on the side of vulnerability.

01:28:36.360 --> 01:28:38.600
Like to me, pride is destructive.

01:28:38.600 --> 01:28:39.540
I think I already,

01:28:43.160 --> 01:28:46.120
yeah, I already have a pretty good engine that says like,

01:28:47.880 --> 01:28:49.240
life is awesome.

01:28:49.240 --> 01:28:50.960
I don't need help for that.

01:28:50.960 --> 01:28:51.800
That's fine.

01:28:51.800 --> 01:28:52.800
That one is working.

01:28:52.800 --> 01:28:57.800
It's the, I just feel like the way to face the world

01:28:58.600 --> 01:29:01.160
that's full of uncertainty that could be full of cruelty

01:29:01.160 --> 01:29:03.920
is with humility and gratitude.

01:29:03.920 --> 01:29:07.920
I don't know, this pride thing, it feels like,

01:29:07.920 --> 01:29:09.760
I know that for a lot of people,

01:29:09.760 --> 01:29:14.760
it's really important to really work on pride

01:29:15.040 --> 01:29:17.920
to make sure they don't crumble under the pressure

01:29:17.920 --> 01:29:21.120
of like, they don't give into the sense of security

01:29:21.120 --> 01:29:22.200
that destroys them.

01:29:22.200 --> 01:29:25.160
But I just, for me, empirically speaking,

01:29:25.160 --> 01:29:29.080
I seem to be happier facing the world with humility

01:29:29.080 --> 01:29:30.120
and just being grateful.

01:29:30.120 --> 01:29:32.360
The pride I'm really worried about.

01:29:32.360 --> 01:29:35.960
Like, it just, it feels more destructive than anything.

01:29:35.960 --> 01:29:38.080
See, what I think, as you're telling me that,

01:29:38.080 --> 01:29:39.120
and I wanna be presumptuous,

01:29:39.120 --> 01:29:42.200
but I make some thoughts or some conclusions that tell me,

01:29:42.200 --> 01:29:44.440
hey, you're in a pretty healthy place, right?

