we're living miles into the envy, you know, land, right?

01:30:08.200 --> 01:30:11.420
So you're describing a healthy vulnerability,

01:30:11.420 --> 01:30:14.280
but then my brain says that's because on the other side

01:30:14.280 --> 01:30:16.280
of the seesaw, so to speak,

01:30:16.280 --> 01:30:18.920
has to be a healthy sense of self,

01:30:18.920 --> 01:30:21.280
whether we call it self-esteem or healthy pride.

01:30:21.280 --> 01:30:24.320
And then I'll say what I think is the evidence for that

01:30:24.320 --> 01:30:27.240
is you describe the negative voice, right?

01:30:27.240 --> 01:30:29.280
