01:32:16.840 --> 01:32:19.600
well, I think it's a really important fact, right?

01:32:19.600 --> 01:32:20.920
That there are some people,

01:32:20.920 --> 01:32:23.160
like a significant subset of people

01:32:23.160 --> 01:32:25.960
who get happier as they get older.

01:32:25.960 --> 01:32:28.600
