It's linked to say, let's say vulnerability versus pride.

01:32:50.200 --> 01:32:51.520
Like there's a good balance there, right?

01:32:51.520 --> 01:32:54.400
There's a lot of humility, there's a lot of self-esteem.

01:32:54.400 --> 01:32:57.560
The person is spending a lot of time standing back

01:32:57.560 --> 01:32:59.960
from the tapestry and looking at it, right?

01:32:59.960 --> 01:33:02.800
And what can come into people

01:33:02.800 --> 01:33:04.560
is in sort of a sense of equanimity.

01:33:04.560 --> 01:33:06.560
Like I sort of understand, you know,

01:33:06.560 --> 01:33:08.680
I'm being the best person I can be, you know,

01:33:08.680 --> 01:33:10.520
and that's not always even great.

01:33:10.520 --> 01:33:12.280
