01:33:13.600 --> 01:33:17.880
But look, I'm being who I'm choosing to be, right?

01:33:17.880 --> 01:33:19.640
And that doesn't have to be in some big way.

01:33:19.640 --> 01:33:22.280
I'm not saying that means any one specific thing.

01:33:22.280 --> 01:33:23.280
You know, that can mean the person

01:33:23.280 --> 01:33:25.680
who's taking care of their cat and tending their garden.

01:33:25.680 --> 01:33:26.840
Like that's enough.

01:33:26.840 --> 01:33:29.520
We have to have, you know, love the ability

01:33:29.520 --> 01:33:31.440
