01:33:34.480 --> 01:33:36.360
to make things different out into the world

01:33:36.360 --> 01:33:37.580
and make things better.

01:33:37.580 --> 01:33:41.000
And if we're doing that, we get happier across time

01:33:41.520 --> 01:33:44.480
