02:12:40.640 --> 02:12:43.040
that every now and then it will happen

02:12:43.040 --> 02:12:46.680
that someone will come and they'll say something.

02:12:46.680 --> 02:12:48.760
Usually it's very early on in the process,

02:12:48.760 --> 02:12:50.640
they'll say something they've never said before,

02:12:50.680 --> 02:12:55.000
and they immediately are in an entirely different place

02:12:55.000 --> 02:12:57.160
and they may have been for decades, right?

02:12:57.160 --> 02:12:59.000
And I can remember a person saying

02:12:59.000 --> 02:13:02.920
that the coach had raped him and just saying it.

02:13:02.920 --> 02:13:06.920
This was decades before and everything was different.

02:13:06.920 --> 02:13:08.800
I'm not saying everything is now as perfect,

02:13:08.800 --> 02:13:10.000
but his life was in a different way.

02:13:10.000 --> 02:13:12.760
As soon as he said it, he could see how daily he thought

02:13:12.760 --> 02:13:15.240
that person did that to this child.

02:13:15.240 --> 02:13:16.480
The child was me.

02:13:16.480 --> 02:13:18.560
He'd never thought it until he said it out loud

02:13:18.560 --> 02:13:20.040
because his mind was going over and over

02:13:20.440 --> 02:13:22.720
with why it was his fault, what he did to deserve it,

02:13:22.720 --> 02:13:25.920
how he kept going back, so it must be his fault.

02:13:25.920 --> 02:13:28.080
It was as soon as he put words to it,

02:13:28.080 --> 02:13:29.640
he saw the truth of it

02:13:29.640 --> 02:13:32.920
and it was a bifurcation in the path of life then.

02:13:32.920 --> 02:13:35.360
And any therapist has stories like that,

02:13:35.360 --> 02:13:36.880
which just shows the immense power

02:13:36.880 --> 02:13:40.320
that it can even be that just uttering the words

02:13:40.320 --> 02:13:44.160
makes just a cascade of change all at once.

02:13:44.160 --> 02:13:46.560
Just saying those words to another human being.

02:13:47.560 --> 02:13:51.600
It makes you wonder what that compulsive loop

02:13:51.600 --> 02:13:53.160
that happens in our heads

02:13:55.000 --> 02:13:57.600
until it's brought to the surface.

02:13:57.600 --> 02:13:58.840
It's so interesting.

02:13:58.840 --> 02:14:00.640
Entirely non-productive the loops.

02:14:00.640 --> 02:14:03.080
And sometimes even if we put, what would I say to another?

02:14:03.080 --> 02:14:04.360
Let me write it down.

02:14:04.360 --> 02:14:06.880
It can get rid of those loops in our brains.

02:14:06.880 --> 02:14:09.560
Is it any even thought of outward expression

02:14:09.560 --> 02:14:11.840
is the enemy of those internal

02:14:11.840 --> 02:14:14.280
persecutory negative thought loops?

02:14:14.280 --> 02:14:15.980
How do you find a good therapist?

