I tend to think of, listen, I'm a fan of podcasts.

02:14:22.360 --> 02:14:23.920
I'm a fan of conversations.

02:14:23.920 --> 02:14:25.960
It feels like a, you know,

02:14:25.960 --> 02:14:29.160
it's like finding a good friend or something.

02:14:29.160 --> 02:14:30.760
It feels like a difficult journey.

02:14:31.760 --> 02:14:32.760
Maybe I'm wrong in that,

02:14:32.760 --> 02:14:34.600
but it just feels like such a,

02:14:35.920 --> 02:14:38.560
it feels like a partnership, a journey together

02:14:38.560 --> 02:14:43.560
versus like some very simple clinical procedure.

02:14:44.000 --> 02:14:45.440
Well, the first thing I would say

02:14:45.440 --> 02:14:47.720
