02:21:35.000 --> 02:21:36.080
They might need it over months.

02:21:36.080 --> 02:21:37.760
They might need it over years.

02:21:37.760 --> 02:21:39.800
But if I'm understanding correctly,

02:21:39.800 --> 02:21:42.000
you're describing something that is

02:21:42.000 --> 02:21:44.600
like a real human engagement, right?

02:21:44.600 --> 02:21:49.160
And I work in a field that for years and years and years,

02:21:49.200 --> 02:21:52.560
the patient didn't get to see the therapist was sitting

02:21:52.560 --> 02:21:55.000
in a place that was sitting behind the person, right?

02:21:55.000 --> 02:21:57.480
So that's not, of course, the only tradition

02:21:57.480 --> 02:21:59.480
and there are aspects of that tradition

02:21:59.480 --> 02:22:01.080
that can be very humanized,

02:22:01.080 --> 02:22:04.640
but the idea that we're supposed to not be human.

02:22:04.640 --> 02:22:06.600
I mean, this medicine is shot through with this, right?

02:22:06.600 --> 02:22:07.840
That the doctor's supposed to be God

02:22:07.840 --> 02:22:09.280
and it protects the doctor.

02:22:09.280 --> 02:22:11.200
And that makes its way into therapy

02:22:11.200 --> 02:22:15.100
and the idea of the superiority the therapist knows more.

02:22:16.440 --> 02:22:18.440
I mean, in some ways, yes,

02:22:18.440 --> 02:22:21.320
but the idea is like to know more about mechanical things,

02:22:21.320 --> 02:22:25.080
like to know more about like facts and knowledge,

02:22:25.080 --> 02:22:26.720
not as a human being, right?

02:22:26.720 --> 02:22:30.720
If we approach therapy as a collaborative human endeavor,

02:22:30.720 --> 02:22:31.560
right?

02:22:31.560 --> 02:22:33.160
Where if we're gonna do it together,

02:22:33.160 --> 02:22:35.360
of course I'm gonna learn from you too, right?

02:22:35.360 --> 02:22:36.680
I mean, we're two human beings

02:22:36.680 --> 02:22:38.280
and we're talking about things that are deep

02:22:38.280 --> 02:22:41.720
and personal and intimate and I'm not gonna participate

02:22:41.720 --> 02:22:44.680
in a way that makes it like about me as much as it's

02:22:44.680 --> 02:22:46.440
about you, but we're two humans

02:22:46.440 --> 02:22:48.800
and what's gone on in me may have relevance

02:22:48.800 --> 02:22:50.480
and sharing it may have relevance.

02:22:50.480 --> 02:22:53.280
And at times you doing something back

02:22:53.280 --> 02:22:54.720
for me may have relevance.

